snippet.title: ▲Nø♦C1iP▲ Walkthrough
snippet.description:
This is a walkthrough of the game "▲Nø♦C1iP▲", also known as "Nø C1iP" or "No Clip".

Play the game here: https://jsqrs.itch.io/n0c1ip

You can visit my Patreon page if you want or something:
https://www.patreon.com/awalkthroughlife

Game created by  jack squires
Music by taylor shechet
___________
Game description (from creator):
*seizure warning*

explore a landscape of disfigured shapes and distorted views.

made for the game jolt's glitch jam

exhibited at cluster new music + integrated arts festival 2015
